Symbol.Script_3D:
! Tube
if gs_detlevel_3D=`Откл.` then End if gs_detlevel_3D=`Простой` then gs_resol=18
if gs_shadow then shadow on else shadow off endif
if GLOB_CONTEXT<20 or GLOB_CONTEXT>40 then resol gs_resol else resol 12 endif
pen gs_cont_pen
unID=1
hotspot 0,0,0,unID : unID=unID+1
!!-----------------------!! !! Base Geometry Editing !! !!-----------------------!!
if edit_mode=`Координаты` then hotspot 0,0,zzyzx,unID,dist_x,1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot -1,0,zzyzx,unID,dist_x,3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot dist_x,0,zzyzx,unID,dist_x,2 : unID=unID+1
hotspot dist_x,0,0,unID,zzyzx,1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot dist_x,0,-1,unID,zzyzx,3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot dist_x,0,zzyzx,unID,zzyzx,2 : unID=unID+1 else hotspot 0,0,0,unID,angle_1,6 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 1,0,0,unID,angle_1,4+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0,-1,0,unID,angle_1,7 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0.5*tube_length*cos(angle_1),0,0.5*tube_length*sin(angle_1),unID,angle_1,5 : unID=unID+1
roty 90-angle_1
hotspot 0,0,0,unID,tube_length,1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0,0,-1,unID,tube_length,3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0,0,tube_length,unID,tube_length,2 : unID=unID+1
del 1 endif
roty 90-angle_1
!!------------------------------!! !! Structural Dimension Editing !! !!------------------------------!!
hotspot 0,0,0,unID,radius_1,1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot -1,0,0,unID,radius_1,3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot radius_1,0,0,unID,radius_1,2 : unID=unID+1
hotspot 0,0,0,unID,radius_1,1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 1,0,0,unID,radius_1,3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot -radius_1,0,0,unID,radius_1,2 : unID=unID+1
hotspot 0,0,0,unID,radius_1,1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0,-1,0,unID,radius_1,3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0,radius_1,0,unID,radius_1,2 : unID=unID+1
hotspot 0,0,0,unID,radius_1,1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0,1,0,unID,radius_1,3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0,-radius_1,0,unID,radius_1,2 : unID=unID+1
hotspot 0,0,tube_length,unID,radius_1,1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot -1,0,tube_length,unID,radius_1,3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot radius_1,0,tube_length,unID,radius_1,2 : unID=unID+1
hotspot 0,0,tube_length,unID,radius_1,1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 1,0,tube_length,unID,radius_1,3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot -radius_1,0,tube_length,unID,radius_1,2 : unID=unID+1
hotspot 0,0,tube_length,unID,radius_1,1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0,-1,tube_length,unID,radius_1,3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0,radius_1,tube_length,unID,radius_1,2 : unID=unID+1
hotspot 0,0,tube_length,unID,radius_1,1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0,1,tube_length,unID,radius_1,3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0,-radius_1,tube_length,unID,radius_1,2 : unID=unID+1
!----------! ! Geometry ! !----------!
material gs_ifc_mat group "cylind" cylind tube_length,radius_1 endgroup !!!!placegroup "elbow"
if tube_thk>0 and tube_thk<radius_1 then group "hole" addz -0.05 cylind tube_length+0.10,radius_1-tube_thk del 1 endgroup !!!!placegroup "hole"
tub=subgroup("cylind","hole") placegroup tub else placegroup "cylind" endif del 1
end
Symbol.Script_2D:
! Tube
pen gs_cont_pen
unID=1 hotspot2 0,0,unID : unID=unID+1
!if edit_mode=`Coordinate` then hotspot2 0,0,unID,dist_x,1+256 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 -1,0,unID,dist_x,3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 dist_x,0,unID,dist_x,2 : unID=unID+1 !else ! hotspot2 0,0,unID : unID=unID+1 ! hotspot2 dist_x,0,unID : unID=unID+1 !endif
!!----------------!! !! Radius Editing !! !!----------------!!
hotspot2 0,0,unID,radius_1,1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 0,-1,unID,radius_1,3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 0,radius_1,unID,radius_1,2 : unID=unID+1
hotspot2 0,0,unID,radius_1,1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 0,1,unID,radius_1,3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 0,-radius_1,unID,radius_1,2 : unID=unID+1
if abs(angle_1-90)<eps then hotspot2 0,0,unID,radius_1,1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 -1,0,unID,radius_1,3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 radius_1,0,unID,radius_1,2 : unID=unID+1
hotspot2 0,0,unID,radius_1,1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 1,0,unID,radius_1,3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 -radius_1,0,unID,radius_1,2 : unID=unID+1 else hotspot2 dist_x,0,unID,radius_1,1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 dist_x,-1,unID,radius_1,3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 dist_x,radius_1,unID,radius_1,2 : unID=unID+1
hotspot2 dist_x,0,unID,radius_1,1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 dist_x,1,unID,radius_1,3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 dist_x,-radius_1,unID,radius_1,2 : unID=unID+1 endif
!!-------------------!! !! Thickness Editing !! !!-------------------!!
hotspot2 0,radius_1,unID,tube_thk,1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 0,radius_1+1,unID,tube_thk,3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 0,radius_1-tube_thk,unID,tube_thk,2 : unID=unID+1
hotspot2 0,-radius_1,unID,tube_thk,1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 0,-radius_1-1,unID,tube_thk,3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 0,-radius_1+tube_thk,unID,tube_thk,2 : unID=unID+1
if abs(angle_1-90)<eps then hotspot2 radius_1,0,unID,tube_thk,1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 radius_1+1,0,unID,tube_thk,3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 radius_1-tube_thk,0,unID,tube_thk,2 : unID=unID+1
hotspot2 -radius_1,0,unID,tube_thk,1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 -radius_1-1,0,unID,tube_thk,3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 -radius_1+tube_thk,0,unID,tube_thk,2 : unID=unID+1 else hotspot2 dist_x,radius_1,unID,tube_thk,1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 dist_x,radius_1+1,unID,tube_thk,3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 dist_x,radius_1-tube_thk,unID,tube_thk,2 : unID=unID+1
hotspot2 dist_x,-radius_1,unID,tube_thk,1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 dist_x,-radius_1-1,unID,tube_thk,3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot2 dist_x,-radius_1+tube_thk,unID,tube_thk,2 : unID=unID+1 endif
!!----------!! !! Geometry !! !!----------!!
mask=7
fill gs_fill_type
if abs(angle_1)<eps then poly2_b 5, mask, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0, radius_1, 1, 0, -radius_1, 1, dist_x, -radius_1, 1, dist_x, radius_1, 1, 0, radius_1, -1
hotline2 0, radius_1,0, -radius_1 hotline2 0, -radius_1,dist_x, -radius_1 hotline2 dist_x, -radius_1,dist_x, radius_1 hotline2 dist_x, radius_1,0, radius_1
line_type gs_DashedLine line2 0,radius_1-tube_thk,dist_x,radius_1-tube_thk line2 0,-radius_1+tube_thk,dist_x,-radius_1+tube_thk hotline2 0,radius_1-tube_thk,dist_x,radius_1-tube_thk hotline2 0,-radius_1+tube_thk,dist_x,-radius_1+tube_thk
if gs_axis then pen gs_axis_pen line_type gs_axis_line line2 0,0,dist_x,0 hotline2 0,0,dist_x,0 endif pen gs_cont_pen
else if abs(angle_1-90)<eps then poly2_b 2, mask, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0, 0, 901, radius_1, 360, 4001
hotarc2 0,0,radius_1,0,180 hotarc2 0,0,radius_1,180,360
poly2_b 2, mask, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0, 0, 901, radius_1-tube_thk, 360, 4001
hotarc2 0,0,radius_1-tube_thk,0,180 hotarc2 0,0,radius_1-tube_thk,180,360
FILL gs_fill_tipe x = sin(32.75) * (radius_1-tube_thk) y = cos(32.75) * (radius_1-tube_thk) poly2_b{5} 7, 1, 0, 3, gs_fill_pen, gs_fill_pen, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 1, 0, -x, -y, 1, (radius_1-tube_thk) * 0.15*2, - (radius_1-tube_thk) * 0.15*2, 900, 0, -155, 4001, y, x, 1, 0, 0, 900, 0, 205, 4001, -x, -y, 1 else mul2 cos(90-angle_1),1 poly2_b 2, mask, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0, 0, 901, radius_1, 360, 4001
hotarc2 0,0,radius_1,0,180 hotarc2 0,0,radius_1,180,360
del 1
line_type gs_line_type poly2_b 5, mask, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0, -radius_1, 1, dist_x, -radius_1, 0, dist_x, radius_1, 1, 0, radius_1, 0, 0, -radius_1, -1
hotline2 0, -radius_1,dist_x, -radius_1 hotline2 dist_x, -radius_1,dist_x, radius_1 hotline2 dist_x, radius_1,0, radius_1 hotline2 0, radius_1,0, -radius_1
line_type gs_DashedLine line2 0,radius_1-tube_thk,dist_x,radius_1-tube_thk line2 0,-radius_1+tube_thk,dist_x,-radius_1+tube_thk hotline2 0,radius_1-tube_thk,dist_x,radius_1-tube_thk hotline2 0,-radius_1+tube_thk,dist_x,-radius_1+tube_thk
if gs_axis then pen gs_axis_pen line_type gs_axis_line line2 0,0,dist_x,0 hotline2 0,0,dist_x,0 endif pen gs_cont_pen
mul2 cos(90-angle_1),1 poly2_b 2, mask, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0, 0, 901, radius_1-tube_thk, 360, 4001
hotarc2 0,0,radius_1-tube_thk,0,180 hotarc2 0,0,radius_1-tube_thk,180,360
del 1
add2 dist_x,0 mul2 cos(90-angle_1),1 poly2_b 2, mask, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0, 0, 901, radius_1, 360, 4001
hotarc2 0,0,radius_1,0,180 hotarc2 0,0,radius_1,180,360
poly2_b 2, mask, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0, 0, 901, radius_1-tube_thk, 360, 4001
hotarc2 0,0,radius_1-tube_thk,0,180 hotarc2 0,0,radius_1-tube_thk,180,360
del 2 endif endif
